description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Quick Bursts Row' from the channel Nick Karwoski.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The The Firestarter vibe means Fast, explosive, and electrifying. Short but devastating. This is especially good for When you only have 10-20 minutes but want to give 1000%. The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Reach high rhythms for short bursts with Nick as you make your way on the race course in Norway. 

Max rhythm: 32+, Format: HIIT ...
